SUMMARY:Kaleidoscope Play & Learn / 万花筒游戏和学习@笔架山分店 / 萬花筒遊戲和學習@筆架山分店
DTSTAMP:20260413T004139Z
DTSTART:20260414T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Tuesday\, April 14\, 2026\, 10:30am - 12pm\n\nChildren listen t
	o multilingual stories\, sing songs and do simple arts and crafts with the
	ir caregivers during the group time. There is also a play time for childre
	n to explore various toys and play activities.\n\nEvent is in English and 
	Mandarin.\n\n-------------------------------------------------------------
	----------------------\n\n萬花筒邊玩邊學®: 孩子與他們的照顧者在小組中一起聽多種語言故事、唱歌並做簡單的手工。萬花筒邊玩
	邊學®也是一個提供孩子們探索各種玩具和遊戲活動的時間。\n\n本活動將以國語和英語進行。\n\n--------------------------
	---------------------------------------------------------\n\n万花筒边玩边学®: 孩子与
	他们的照顾者在小组中一起听多种语言故事、唱歌并做简单的手工。万花筒边玩边学®也是一个提供給孩子们探索各种玩具和游戏活动的时间。\n\n本次活动将以普
	通话和英语进行。\n\nLocation Link:\n\nBeacon Hill Branch\n\nRoom Location: Meeting
	 Room\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is not required / 注册不是必须的。\n\
	nDetailed Description: Kaleidoscope Play & Learn helps families prepare th
	eir young children for success in school and life. This program\, reaches 
	families in their neighborhoods and in their home languages weekly. Kids a
	nd their caregivers take part in play activities that include stories\, mu
	sic\, game or crafts to support children's early learning.\, Community ser
	vices\, parenting education\, and child care resources available to help p
	arents and caregivers raise healthy children.\, Thanks to our partners\n\n
	Chinese Information and Service Center \\(CISC\\)\n\nand\n\nService Center
	 .\,\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------
	-----------------\, 雙語學前幼兒樂園活動協助家庭為幼兒提前適應學校和生活環境。每星期在不同的社區以家庭語言進行活動\,透過年齡適
	切的活動方式，包括遊戲﹑雙語兒歌﹑故事﹑手工﹑玩具等，支持兒童早期教學。\, 提供社區服務﹑家庭教育及育兒資源，讓幼兒家長及其照顧者培育健康活潑的孩
	子。\, 感謝我們的合作夥伴  Chinese Information and Service Center \\(CISC\\) 。\,\n\n-
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------
	--------\, 双语学前幼儿乐园活动协助家庭为幼儿提前适应学校和生活环境。每星期在不同的社区以家庭语言进行活动\,透过年龄适切的活动方式，包括
	游戏﹑双语儿歌﹑故事﹑手工﹑玩具等，支持儿童早期教学。\, 提供社区服务﹑家庭教育及育儿资源，让幼儿家长及其照顾者培育健康活泼的孩子。\, 感谢我们
	的合作伙伴  Chinese Information and Service Center \\(CISC\\) 。\,\n\nEvent Logi
	stics: This group is open to children of all abilities\, ages 0 to 5 years
	 old.\, Kaleidoscope Play & Learn is for Family\, Friend & Neighbor Caregi
	vers\, Parents\, and the children in their care. This is not a drop-off pr
	ogram and it is not agood fit for daycare centers\, preschools\, or other 
	childcare organizations.\, Find out more about\n\nEarly Learning & Story T
	ime\n\nprograms.\,\n\n----------------------------------------------------
	-------------------------------\, 活動對象為0至5歲各種能力的兒童。萬花筒遊戲與學習 "適合家庭、朋友、鄰居的照顧
	者、父母和他們照顧的孩子。 这不是一个投递计划，也不适合日托中心、学前班或其他托儿机构。\,\n\n------------------------
