BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:ejw7usKUhaVthaoQgdIl5
SUMMARY:Free Tax Help
DTSTAMP:20260413T004139Z
DTSTART:20260415T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Wednesday\, April 15\, 2026\, 10am - 1:30pm\n\nTrained voluntee
	rs will be available to answer questions and prepare personal tax returns.
	\n\nLocation Link:\n\nBroadview Branch\n\nRoom Location: Meeting Room\n\nD
	etailed Description: Drop-in tax help is offered on a first-come\, first-s
	erved basis. This service is free and available to individuals only. The f
	ree service is not available for business tax returns. To receive tax help
	\, bring the following documents:\,\n\nRequired Documents:\n\nPhoto identi
	fication\, Social Security cards or Individual Taxpayer Identification Num
	bers \\(ITIN\\) for everyone listed on the tax return.\, Proof of income\,
	 for example\, W2s and 1099s \\(Social Security benefits\\)\, Official doc
	uments on Social Security Administration letterhead\, Medicare card \\(if 
	Social Security number is followed by an "A"\\)\, Be prepared to provide i
	nformation about health care coverage for each person on the return.\,\n\n
	Recommended:\n\nLast year's tax return\, if available\, Bank account and r
	outing numbers for direct deposit of refunds\, Photocopies or computer pri
	nt-outs of any of these documents willbe accepted.\, Due to federal budget
	 cuts the IRS is unable to provide the Library with certain tax forms and 
	instruction booklets.\, Most IRS forms are available online at\n\nwww.irs.
	gov .\, You may make free black-and-white prints of the forms from Library
	 computers:\n\nwww.spl.org/Print \, Thanks to our partner\n\nAARP .\n\nEve
	nt Logistics: For eligibility details\, contact AARP at 888-227-7669.\, Un
	ited Way Tax Help locations serve anyone who earned less than $80\,000 in 
	2025.\n\nContact Us: If you have questions about this event\,\n\nAsk Us\n\
	nor call 206-386-4636.\n\nADA Accommodations: We can provide accommodation
	s for people with disabilities at Library events. Please\n\ncontactLEAP\n\
	nat least seven days before the event to request accommodations.\, All Lib
	rary programs are free and open to the public.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity
	.com/events/#/details/free-tax-help/18162991/2026-04-15T00\n\nFrom SEAtoda
	y - Arts & Culture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/free-tax-help/18162991/20
	26-04-15T00
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-arts
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H30M
END:VEVENT
